frame Leave a battle

actor Student
activate Student

Student->System: 1: requestBattlePage()

activate System
System-->Student: 2: show(battle-page)
deactivate System

Student->System: 3: leaveBattle(battle)

activate System
alt signedIn == false
System-->Student: 4: show(not-signed-in Message)
System-->Student: 5: show(battle-page)
else hasJoinedBattle == false
System-->Student: 6: show(not-joined-battle Message)
System-->Student: 7: show(battle-page)
else 
System->System: 8: removeStudent(student)
Student<--System: 9: ack
end

deactivate System
deactivate Student

